\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"the main event\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"bookmarks\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"The Independent\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice On a summer's morning in June last year, French police arrived unannounced at the house of the Paris 2024 CEO, Etienne Thobois.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.162725896862938e-50, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 657, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.128357707105895e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\", \"score\": 0.9999993218032185, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Etienne Thobois\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 560}, {\"ngram\": \"a summer's morning\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the house\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They rummaged through his possessions and seized documents as part of synchronised raids on the organising committee headquarters, and the offices of companies awarded contracts to help deliver the Games.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his possessions\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"documents\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"synchronised raids\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee headquarters\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the offices\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"companies\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"contracts\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The investigation into \\\"illegal conflict of interest, misuse of public funds and favouritism\\\" remains ongoing, and no charges have been brought against Thobois or anyone else involved.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The investigation\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"illegal conflict\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"misuse\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"public funds\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"favouritism\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"no charges\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There has been no public statement in months, and whenThe Independentcontacted the French National Financial Prosecutor's Office (PNF) last week, we were told that the inquiry \\\"continues with analysis by investigators of the numerous documents seized\\\" and isunlikely to conclude before the Olympics begin.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no public statement\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"the French National Financial Prosecutor's Office\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"PNF\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"the inquiry\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"analysis\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"investigators\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"the numerous documents\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be natural to be cynical, especially when corruption was uncovered at the heart of boththe RioandTokyo Games.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"corruption\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"boththe RioandTokyo Games\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But PNF director Jean-Francois Bohnert said that he does not expect to uncover \\\"the most serious cases of corruption\\\", and Thobois is adamant that the Paris Olympics are a clean operation and will be proved so.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Fascist_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"PNF\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Fascist_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Fascist_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most serious cases\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"corruption\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"a clean operation\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From the start, we put in all kinds of processes in order to be exemplary,\\\" he tellsThe Independent.\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"all kinds\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"processes\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then it is normal [that] we are very much controlled.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have all kinds of control in various areas, and it's a good thing.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all kinds\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"various areas\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"a good thing\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's part of an inquiry.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"an inquiry\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot tell you more because I do not know more.\\\"\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thobois was a founder of marketing agency Keneo, which was awarded \\u20ac2m in contracts linked to Paris's Olympic bid.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2121, \"end\": 2126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4258095793728793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"a founder\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"marketing agency\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"Keneo\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u20ac2m\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"contracts\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says he ended all involvement with Keneo before those deals were ever discussed.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all involvement\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"Keneo\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"those deals\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually sold all my [shares] before taking the job of CEO of the bid committee so I do not have any relation with the company since, I think, 15 June 2015.\\\"\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all my [shares\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"CEO\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"the bid committee\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"any relation\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was shocked when investigators came to his home.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"investigators\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"his home\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a surprise,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a surprise\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I guess it's part of the job, let us put it that way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thobois is sitting in his office at Paris 2024 headquarters just a few months out from the start of the Games.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2563, \"end\": 2573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.128357707105895e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2534}, {\"ngram\": \"his office\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The investigation has been an unwelcome distraction from what has otherwise been a relatively smooth build-up to these Olympics.\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The investigation\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"an unwelcome distraction\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"a relatively smooth build-up\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is about this time in the Olympic cycle when everything tends to go wrong: think of Tokyo's spiralling costs, Zika fears before Rio, the G4S security scandal before London.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2854, \"end\": 2859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.332511302785578e-18, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2898, \"end\": 2901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.619845491428607, \"rank\": 0.6133052563050002, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999967822077, \"rank\": 3.2177848747157757e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about this time\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic cycle\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2825}, {\"ngram\": \"Zika\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"the G4S security scandal\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Excitement tends to give way to a creeping sense of anxiety.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Excitement\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2971}, {\"ngram\": \"a creeping sense\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So no wonder Thobois is smiling as he describes the air of calm around these Olympics.\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"So no wonder\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"calm\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly 8 million tickets have been sold, with only a few venues struggling to sell out - mostly football stadiums outside Paris.\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3214, \"end\": 3219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4258095793728793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nearly 8 million tickets\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3116}, {\"ngram\": \"only a few venues\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3155}, {\"ngram\": \"football stadiums\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The few pieces of infrastructure being built for the Games are on schedule.\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The few pieces\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3253}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"schedule\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two biggest building projects, the Olympic Village and the Aquatic Centre, will open in the coming weeks.\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3336, \"end\": 3351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8987663997220466e-32, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The two biggest building projects\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3330}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatic Centre\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3374}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming weeks\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This streamlined Olympic plan was at the heart of Paris's successful bid, in which Thobois's team promised not to build an army of white elephants but to harness the city's current facilities to deliver a Games using 95 per cent existing or temporary venues.\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3458, \"end\": 3463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4258095793728793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3454}, {\"ngram\": \"Thobois's team\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3505}, {\"ngram\": \"an army\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"white elephants\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3554}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's current facilities\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3599}, {\"ngram\": \"a Games\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3618}, {\"ngram\": \"95 per cent existing or temporary venues\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given most of the venues are close to the centre of Paris, there was no need to build vast new transport networks either.\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3719, \"end\": 3724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4258095793728793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the venues\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3691}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3715}, {\"ngram\": \"no need\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3743}, {\"ngram\": \"vast new transport networks\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The infrastructure, including transport infrastructure, is something we do not have to worry about in respect to previous games, so that's already a fantastic relief,\\\" says Thobois.\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The infrastructure\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3808}, {\"ngram\": \"transport infrastructure\", \"from\": 3820, \"to\": 3844}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 3899}, {\"ngram\": \"previous games\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3917}, {\"ngram\": \"a fantastic relief\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 3955}, {\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 3970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is what Paris hopes will make these Games unique, by creating an Olympics woven into the existing fabric of the city.\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 4095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3986, \"end\": 3991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4258095793728793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 4008, \"to\": 4019}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 4040, \"to\": 4051}, {\"ngram\": \"the existing fabric\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4082}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds of thousands of spectators will line the River Seine for an opening ceremony brought out of the usual stadium environment and laid out in Paris itself.\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4146, \"end\": 4157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 4243, \"end\": 4248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4258095793728793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hundreds of thousands\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4117}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4131}, {\"ngram\": \"an opening ceremony\", \"from\": 4162, \"to\": 4181}, {\"ngram\": \"the usual stadium environment\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cycling road races will pass through the centre of the city, as will the marathons, which for the first time will also see 40,000 ordinary runners tackle the route, hours after the official men's race has concluded.\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cycling road races\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4279}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4308}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4320}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathons\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4343}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 4355, \"to\": 4369}, {\"ngram\": \"40,000 ordinary runners\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4424}, {\"ngram\": \"the official men's race\", \"from\": 4438, \"to\": 4461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It will be probably the first Games where we will bereallyat the heart of the city,\\\" says Thobois.\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first Games\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4513}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 4539, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4560}, {\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 4568, \"to\": 4575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Security is at the heart of everything we do ... not one stone has been left unturned Another pillar of Paris's bid was that any investment would be focused on Seine-Saint-Denis, a deprived northern suburb and the second poorest neighbourhood in France, an area of high crime and poverty, and low education and life expectancy.\", \"from\": 4578, \"to\": 4906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4683, \"end\": 4688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4258095793728793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4825, \"end\": 4831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999860135411275, \"rank\": 0.00013125860537255437, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Security\", \"from\": 4578, \"to\": 4586}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 4593, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4606, \"to\": 4616}, {\"ngram\": \"not one stone\", \"from\": 4627, \"to\": 4640}, {\"ngram\": \"Another pillar\", \"from\": 4664, \"to\": 4678}, {\"ngram\": \"any investment\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4717}, {\"ngram\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4755}, {\"ngram\": \"a deprived northern suburb\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4783}, {\"ngram\": \"the second poorest neighbourhood\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4820}, {\"ngram\": \"an area\", \"from\": 4832, \"to\": 4839}, {\"ngram\": \"high crime\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4853}, {\"ngram\": \"poverty\", \"from\": 4858, \"to\": 4865}, {\"ngram\": \"low education and life expectancy\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is unsurprisingly not a hotbed for swimming, with only 50 per cent of children under 11 able to swim.\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 5011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hotbed\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 4940}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 4953}, {\"ngram\": \"only 50 per cent\", \"from\": 4960, \"to\": 4976}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 4980, \"to\": 4988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this is where the brand new \\u00a3150m Paris 2024 Aquatic Centre has been built, along with nine new training pools across the region, with the aim of transforming local lives.\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5050, \"end\": 5060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.128357707105895e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 5030, \"to\": 5039}, {\"ngram\": \"nine new training pools\", \"from\": 5103, \"to\": 5126}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 5134, \"to\": 5144}, {\"ngram\": \"the aim\", \"from\": 5151, \"to\": 5158}, {\"ngram\": \"local lives\", \"from\": 5175, \"to\": 5186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think about 90 per cent of the infrastructure budget went to Seine-Saint-Denis,\\\" says Thobois.\", \"from\": 5189, \"to\": 5286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5253, \"end\": 5270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 90 per cent\", \"from\": 5198, \"to\": 5215}, {\"ngram\": \"the infrastructure budget\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5244}, {\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 5278, \"to\": 5285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's where we built the [athletes'] village, the media village, the Aquatic Centre, training centres.\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the [athletes'] village\", \"from\": 5310, \"to\": 5333}, {\"ngram\": \"the media village\", \"from\": 5335, \"to\": 5352}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatic Centre\", \"from\": 5354, \"to\": 5372}, {\"ngram\": \"training centres\", \"from\": 5374, \"to\": 5390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is definitely a physical legacy completely concentrated in Seine-Saint-Denis, because that's where the big needs were.\", \"from\": 5392, \"to\": 5513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5454, \"end\": 5471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a physical legacy\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5426}, {\"ngram\": \"the big needs\", \"from\": 5494, \"to\": 5507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are here in Seine-Saint-Denis, our headquarters, we are employing people from the area\\u2026 so we walk the talk.\\\"\", \"from\": 5514, \"to\": 5626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5546}, {\"ngram\": \"our headquarters\", \"from\": 5548, \"to\": 5564}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5589}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 5595, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"the talk\", \"from\": 5616, \"to\": 5624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thobois speaks passionately about the impact the Olympics can have on the wider world.\", \"from\": 5628, \"to\": 5714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 5628, \"to\": 5635}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 5662, \"to\": 5672}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5685}, {\"ngram\": \"the wider world\", \"from\": 5698, \"to\": 5713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a talented badminton player, he competed at the 1996 Olympics in Atlanta.\", \"from\": 5715, \"to\": 5791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5783, \"end\": 5790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.107361256419551e-20, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a talented badminton player\", \"from\": 5718, \"to\": 5745}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1996 Olympics\", \"from\": 5762, \"to\": 5779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What most struck Thobois was the feeling of entering the Olympic Stadium for the opening ceremony in front of 80,000 people and billions more on TV, as Muhammad Ali famously defied Parkinson's disease to light the torch.\", \"from\": 5792, \"to\": 6012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5944, \"end\": 5956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999987607382939, \"rank\": 1.238291259724276e-06, \"text\": \"Muhammad Ali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 5809, \"to\": 5816}, {\"ngram\": \"the feeling\", \"from\": 5821, \"to\": 5832}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Stadium\", \"from\": 5845, \"to\": 5864}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 5869, \"to\": 5889}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 5893, \"to\": 5898}, {\"ngram\": \"80,000 people\", \"from\": 5902, \"to\": 5915}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 5920, \"to\": 5928}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 5937, \"to\": 5939}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkinson's disease\", \"from\": 5973, \"to\": 5992}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 6002, \"to\": 6011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That particular moment makes you realise that sport is more than just sport, and that the Olympic Games are more than just a sporting event.\", \"from\": 6013, \"to\": 6154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That particular moment\", \"from\": 6014, \"to\": 6036}, {\"ngram\": \"that sport\", \"from\": 6055, \"to\": 6065}, {\"ngram\": \"just sport\", \"from\": 6079, \"to\": 6089}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 6100, \"to\": 6117}, {\"ngram\": \"just a sporting event\", \"from\": 6132, \"to\": 6153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is something beyond that.\", \"from\": 6155, \"to\": 6183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 6161, \"to\": 6170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And with the world that we are living in right now, with all the tension with all that's happening, I think the Olympic movement is needed more than ever.\\\"\", \"from\": 6184, \"to\": 6339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 6193, \"to\": 6202}, {\"ngram\": \"all the tension\", \"from\": 6241, \"to\": 6256}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic movement\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps the greatest threat to his mission is security.\", \"from\": 6341, \"to\": 6396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greatest threat\", \"from\": 6349, \"to\": 6368}, {\"ngram\": \"his mission\", \"from\": 6372, \"to\": 6383}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 6387, \"to\": 6395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games come less than a decade after the deadliest terrorist attack in French history which occurred in multiple sites across Paris, leaving deep scars and a city on edge.\", \"from\": 6397, \"to\": 6571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6471, \"end\": 6485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 6526, \"end\": 6531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4258095793728793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Games\", \"from\": 6397, \"to\": 6406}, {\"ngram\": \"the deadliest terrorist attack\", \"from\": 6437, \"to\": 6467}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple sites\", \"from\": 6504, \"to\": 6518}, {\"ngram\": \"deep scars\", \"from\": 6541, \"to\": 6551}, {\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 6556, \"to\": 6562}, {\"ngram\": \"edge\", \"from\": 6566, \"to\": 6570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, six nights of rioting after the killing of Nahel Merzouk followed months of protests which occasionally spilt over into violence.\", \"from\": 6572, \"to\": 6712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six nights\", \"from\": 6583, \"to\": 6593}, {\"ngram\": \"rioting\", \"from\": 6597, \"to\": 6604}, {\"ngram\": \"the killing\", \"from\": 6611, \"to\": 6622}, {\"ngram\": \"Nahel Merzouk\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6639}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 6649, \"to\": 6655}, {\"ngram\": \"protests\", \"from\": 6659, \"to\": 6667}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 6703, \"to\": 6711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another warning came at the 2022 Champions League final, where choatic scenes left question marks over the ability of French police to handle major events.\", \"from\": 6713, \"to\": 6868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6746, \"end\": 6762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9532474664925396e-34, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}, {\"begin\": 6831, \"end\": 6844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.162725896862938e-50, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another warning\", \"from\": 6713, \"to\": 6728}, {\"ngram\": \"choatic scenes\", \"from\": 6776, \"to\": 6790}, {\"ngram\": \"question marks\", \"from\": 6796, \"to\": 6810}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 6816, \"to\": 6827}, {\"ngram\": \"major events\", \"from\": 6855, \"to\": 6867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The image of France is at stake,\\\" Paris 2024 president Tony Estanguet said recently.\", \"from\": 6869, \"to\": 6954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6883, \"end\": 6889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999860135411275, \"rank\": 0.00013125860537255437, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 6904, \"end\": 6914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.128357707105895e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 6925, \"end\": 6939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The image\", \"from\": 6870, \"to\": 6879}, {\"ngram\": \"stake\", \"from\": 6896, \"to\": 6901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thobois knows no Olympic Games can guarantee safety, but he has faith in the comprehensive security operation for Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 6956, \"to\": 7081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7070, \"end\": 7080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.128357707105895e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thobois\", \"from\": 6956, \"to\": 6963}, {\"ngram\": \"no Olympic Games\", \"from\": 6970, \"to\": 6986}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 7001, \"to\": 7007}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 7020, \"to\": 7025}, {\"ngram\": \"the comprehensive security operation\", \"from\": 7029, \"to\": 7065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Security is at the heart of everything we do,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 7082, \"to\": 7138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Security\", \"from\": 7083, \"to\": 7091}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 7098, \"to\": 7107}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 7111, \"to\": 7121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a huge plan that is being put in place.\", \"from\": 7139, \"to\": 7188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge plan\", \"from\": 7149, \"to\": 7160}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 7182, \"to\": 7187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tens of thousands of people are going to be implemented and not one stone has been left unturned.\", \"from\": 7189, \"to\": 7286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tens of thousands\", \"from\": 7189, \"to\": 7206}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7210, \"to\": 7216}, {\"ngram\": \"not one stone\", \"from\": 7249, \"to\": 7262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not about being confident, it is about being thorough, and to limit the risks that will always remain.\\\"\", \"from\": 7287, \"to\": 7396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the risks\", \"from\": 7361, \"to\": 7370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is hard to imagine that the greatest sporting show on earth, hosted by one of the great European cities, will be anything other than a rip-roaring success.\", \"from\": 7398, \"to\": 7556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greatest sporting show\", \"from\": 7425, \"to\": 7451}, {\"ngram\": \"earth\", \"from\": 7455, \"to\": 7460}, {\"ngram\": \"the great European cities\", \"from\": 7479, \"to\": 7504}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 7514, \"to\": 7522}, {\"ngram\": \"a rip-roaring success\", \"from\": 7534, \"to\": 7555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the investigation into the organising committee's conduct still lingers in the background and it will hang over the Games themselves.\", \"from\": 7557, \"to\": 7694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the investigation\", \"from\": 7561, \"to\": 7578}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee's conduct\", \"from\": 7584, \"to\": 7618}, {\"ngram\": \"the background\", \"from\": 7636, \"to\": 7650}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 7673, \"to\": 7682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It remains shrouded in secrecy and even Thobois has little knowledge of when those questions might be answered.\", \"from\": 7695, \"to\": 7806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"secrecy\", \"from\": 7718, \"to\": 7725}, {\"ngram\": \"even Thobois\", \"from\": 7730, \"to\": 7742}, {\"ngram\": \"little knowledge\", \"from\": 7747, \"to\": 7763}, {\"ngram\": \"those questions\", \"from\": 7772, \"to\": 7787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's all I know - they came and looked and they did their job, and we are fully cooperating.\", \"from\": 7807, \"to\": 7902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their job\", \"from\": 7862, \"to\": 7871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's all I can say.\\\"\", \"from\": 7903, \"to\": 7929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 7931, \"to\": 8161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7982, \"end\": 7993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5064747839691084e-32, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 7936, \"to\": 7967}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 8010, \"to\": 8023}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 8039, \"to\": 8047}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 8063, \"to\": 8075}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 8079, \"to\": 8087}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 8115, \"to\": 8123}, {\"ngram\": \"your browser\", \"from\": 8132, \"to\": 8144}]}]}"